{"word":"αὐτοσχεδόν","slug":"αὐτοσχεδόν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n17949\" key=\"au)tosxedo/n\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">αὐτο-σχεδόν</orth>, <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> <sense id=\"n17949.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">near at hand, hand to hand,</tr_> in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> always of close fight, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ξιφέεσσ᾽ αὐ. οὐτάζοντο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:273\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.273</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">δῄουν ἀλλήλους αὐ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:708\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.708</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αὐ. ὡρμήθησαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:496\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.496</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:293\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.293</biblScope> </bibl>:—once also <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αὐτοσχεδὰ δουρὶ . . ἐπόρουσε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:319\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.319</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὐτοσχέδιος.</foreign> </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n17949.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. gen., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">near, close to,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀλλήλῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:901\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">901</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n17949.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of Time, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">on the spot, at once,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.12</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:148\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.148</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}